OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,FBereaved families have expressed their
OL,7,Ffrustration after new figures showed
OL,8,Fdog attacks have nearly doubled since
OL,9,F2020, and some have questioned if
OL,10,Fbanning certain breeds is effective,
OL,11,FITV News' Sabah Choudhry reports
OL,13,FAdditional reporting by Assistant
OL,14,FProducer Jake Brook
OL,16,FA campaigner who staged a legal
OL,17,Fchallenge of the banning of XL Bullies
OL,18,Fhas said more focus is needed on
OL,19,Fresponsible ownership after figures
OL,20,Frevealed a sharp rise in dog attacks
OL,21,Fsince 2020.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
