OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,FFigures obtained by the Daily Mirror
OL,7,Fshow offences of out-of-control dog
OL,8,Fattacks causing injury recorded by
OL,9,Fpolice have risen from 16,040 in 2020
OL,10,Fto 29,400 last year ` a rise of 83%.
OL,12,FAttacks continued to rise despite a
OL,13,Fban of the XL bully breed, which came
OL,14,Finto force in February 2024, which
OL,15,Fcampaigner Sophie Coulthard says shows
OL,16,Fthe ban has not made people safer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,F"One of the problems that we have at
OL,7,Fthe moment is that there is a
OL,8,Fperceived level of safety by banning a
OL,9,Fcertain type of dog," she tells ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,F"Is it possible that there's been some
OL,13,Fcomplacency among the general public
OL,14,Fover what constitutes a dangerous
OL,15,Fbreed aggressive dog?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,F"I think that because we've had this
OL,7,Fimage of a certain type of dog as
OL,8,Fbeing more aggressive, by the way that
OL,9,Fit looks, perhaps people have become
OL,10,Fmore complacent with other types of
OL,11,Fdogs.
OL,13,F"At the end of the day, any dog can be
OL,14,Faggressive. What a dog looks like does
OL,15,Fnot determine aggression, and that's
OL,16,Fbeen found across all research. So I
OL,17,Fwonder if that plays a part in the
OL,18,Frise."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
