CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,FMs Coulthard director of the Don't Ban
OL,7,FMe, Licence Me campaign group, led a
OL,8,Flegal challenge, which was ultimately
OL,9,Fquashed in the Court of Appeal last
OL,10,Fyear, against the government's banning
OL,11,Fof XL Bullies.
OL,13,FShe suggests that even the term XL
OL,14,FBully, or the way dogs are identified
OL,15,Fas such by authorities, is confusing
OL,16,Fand misleading, adding that her dog,
OL,17,Fand explains why her dog, Billy, does
OL,18,Fnot qualify as an XL.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
