PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,F"An XL bully is not a breed; it's just
OL,7,Fa type and actually is a type of
OL,8,FAmerican bully. It's a size. So, an XL
OL,9,Fbully stands at 20 inches for a male.
OL,10,FThere are other considerations as
OL,11,Fwell, like the size of the head, the
OL,12,Fsize of the chest.
OL,14,F"So, for me, because he just about
OL,15,Fscrapes the height, I (legally)
OL,16,Fexempted him for his safety. But when
OL,17,Fthe police looked at him, they have a
OL,18,Fchecklist and it's as well as height.
OL,26,@wD@WpmwD@_pn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,F"They basically said his head was not
OL,7,Fa bowling ball enough, his chest
OL,8,Fwasn't broad enough. So, whilst he
OL,9,Fstill is an American bully... he's
OL,10,Fjust lucky because he's on the smaller
OL,11,Fside."
OL,13,FMs Coulthard asks why the system deems
OL,14,Fa dog at 19 inches tall as "not
OL,15,Fdangerous" and at 20 inches tall
OL,16,F"dangerous", adding that no credit is
OL,17,Fgiven to "responsible ownership".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
