OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,F"I think any dog in the right hands
OL,7,Fwith the right owner who is
OL,8,Fresponsible can thrive and be a loving
OL,9,Fmember of the family," she adds.
OL,11,F"Don't get me wrong, I watch him
OL,12,Faround kids and, you know, I'm always
OL,13,Fvery careful that they understand
OL,14,Fwhat's acceptable, what's not
OL,15,Facceptable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
