OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,F"My dog has such a good temperament,
OL,7,Fhe's great with children, he loves
OL,8,Feveryone. He changes people. People do
OL,9,FSometimes have a preconceived idea of
OL,10,Fwhat he's going to be like and he wins
OL,11,Fthem over in the end.
OL,13,F"I grew up with bull breeds, so I knew
OL,14,Fthat I was taking on a dog that would
OL,15,Fhave a level of power and strength...
OL,16,FI think if you are taking on a dog
OL,17,Fthat is strong and is powerful, you do
OL,18,Fneed to have an extra level of
OL,19,Fresponsibility that goes with that."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
