OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,FAsked how she thinks the system should
OL,7,Fwork in an ideal world, Ms Coulthard
OL,8,Fsays: "I think the problem with where
OL,9,Fwe are with dogs in the UK at the
OL,10,Fmoment is that it's so polarising.
OL,12,F"We're judging dogs on the way we
OL,13,Flook. We're stereotyping owners based
OL,14,Fon what type of dog they have.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,FIf we move towards a model that
OL,7,Ffocused on responsible breeding,
OL,8,Fresponsible ownership, proper
OL,9,Fenforcement of the law and education,
OL,10,Fthen I think we'd have a much better
OL,11,Fsociety, and I think dogs would be
OL,12,Fhappier and I think the public would
OL,13,Ffeel safer.
OL,15,F"I think what's important is that we
OL,16,Fget across the message that any dog
OL,17,Fcan be aggressive and actually we
OL,18,Fshould be looking at the owners and
OL,19,Fsaying, is that owner walking this dog
OL,20,Fsensibly?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777169008
OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,F"Have they got it on an appropriate
OL,7,Flead? Are they looking at the dog or
OL,8,Fare they on their phone?
OL,10,F"I think if we started to have a bit
OL,11,Fmore of a common-sense approach and
OL,12,Fdog owners did take responsibility for
OL,13,Fhow they are when they're out and
OL,14,Fabout with their dog, then we might
OL,15,Fsee a difference."
OL,17,FLondon saw the highest number of dog
OL,18,Fattacks in 2025, with the Metropolitan
OL,19,FPolice recording 2,530 cases, the
OL,20,FDaily Mirror's Freedom of Information
OL,21,FAct requests to police forces shows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
