OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police recorded the
OL,7,Fsecond highest total with 1,678
OL,8,Fattacks.
OL,10,FEarlier this month a three-month-old
OL,11,FMaggie-May Ann Moody died in
OL,12,FDormanstown, near Redcar, Cleveland,
OL,13,Fafter being bitten by a dog.
OL,15,FArmed police attended and shot a dog
OL,16,Fat the property, with another being
OL,17,Fput down later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
