OL,3,CDon't judge by breed, campaigner says
OL,4,Cas dog attacks rise by 83% since 2020
OL,6,FIn a statement issued to Cleveland
OL,7,FPolice, her family said: "Maggie
OL,8,Fchanged us in so many ways. She was
OL,9,Feverything to us. She gave us meaning
OL,10,Fand purpose every day, and we feel
OL,11,Fempty.
OL,13,F"As parents and a family, we have been
OL,14,Frobbed of a beautiful lifetime and
OL,15,Fmemories with her. Our lives will
OL,16,Fnever be the same again, she will
OL,17,Falways be in our hearts."
